summary: This code file, TCInput.h, is a header file for the TCInput class in the SMG_NothingIsAll project. It defines three methods: rInput, pInput, and hInput, which are used to input data into different parts of the AI system. The except_ps parameter is an array of excluded parameters for the rInput method. The AIAlgNodeBase, AICMVNodeBase, and TOAlgModel classes are used as input parameters in these methods.
